<br>
So, more times then not  I accept or request a dot or 11 pp for Temperance thru Virtue buffs.  Dont do it to be greedy or mean.   Its just the reality of it.<br>
<br>
What I do not appreciate is if Im not /role...getting 10000000 DEMANDS for buffs.  Just cause Im in PoK for one minute does not mean I am there to buff a zone full of people. Normally I have another destination in mind and am just passing thru.  And when LoY came out, I had no need for Temperance.   I was already 65 and had no use for a lvl 44 buff.  I cant tell you the number of times I was called a liar for not having a QUESTED spell.  Finally, one evening while bored.  I quested the stupid spell.  Nice to buff my husband and other friends lower lvl alts with.<br>
