<br>
I havent paid for a buff or rez in a LONG LONG time.  I havent accepted payment for a buff in a LONGER time.  I dont advertise my class. I dont run around PoK holding my snake stick. I always buff people (with the crack of their choice) when I ask for buffs/ports/rez's.<br>
<br>
If you want C3, tough crap.  My C5 lasts 2hrs+ and if thats not long enough either, 1) you are doing tradeskills in which case you are gonna want a break or 2) your group isnt trying hard enough.<br>
<br>
