<br>
I don't ask for it.  If you need a rez, and I have the mana to spare (i.e., not when I'm in a group in the middle of a tough fight), I'll rez you and won't ask for a donation.<br>
<br>
As for buffs, for Guildmates and Group members, I cast Temp on them without expecting a donation.<br>
<br>
However, if someone comes to me and asks for temp, I expect at least enough to cover the dot....now, if I do a drive by Buffing, I don't ask for or expect donations.<br>
<br>
If someone just asks me for buffs and doesn't offer to cover the cost of the dot, they get mana only buffs.<br>
<br>
Again, this all depends on the situation...if I'm in a group in the middle of a fight or am medding to have enough mana, either be willing to wait, or go find someone else. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=558439" target="top">Lledier Hosen</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Dwarven Cleric of Brell - L52 - Dragons of Xev.<br>
